{"type":null,"faqId":31856,"title":"手机是否支持 WLAN 直连？如何操作？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>支持。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以参考如下步骤进行设置：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置 &gt; WLAN”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击或滑动 “WLAN” 后的开关至 “</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98974\" style=\"width:0.28541666in;height:0.20625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，开启 WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击 “WLAN 直连”，同时在需要接受文件的设备上开启 WLAN 直连。手机会自动搜索可连接的设备。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击需要共享的设备名称与之建立连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98975\" style=\"width:5.164583in;height:2.4590278in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98976\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>如果手机与需要共享文件的设备已连接至同一 WLAN 网络，且均已经开启 WLAN直连，则二者无需手动建立 WLAN 直连，可以直接共享文件。（此策略不一定支持其他厂商的设备，连接前请确认其他设备是否支持）。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98977\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6376","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435287939000,"seriesProductName":"DAV-703L","visitedTimes":125,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"wifi直连,wifi共享,共享文件,发送文件,wifi direct","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}